dreaming you are at the same place on different ocasions i had a dream once that i was in a place i have never been before and it was a lovely place where i would like to go one day the next time i dreamt i was at the same place but with my family as if it was like years ago and my grandfather who passed away looking happy and healthy trying to cheer me up and saying goodbye to me i was sad as i was going away then i dreamt again that i was at the same place but with no one else has anyone had a similar dream or knows if there is any meaning behind these family to see your own family in your dream represents security warmth and love consider also the significance of a particular family member or the relationship you have with them death to dream about the death of a loved one suggests that you are lacking a certain aspect or quality that the loved one embodies ask yourself what makes this person special or what do you like about him it is that very quality that you are lacking in your own relationship or circumstances alternatively it indicates that whatever that person represents has no part in your own life places to dream of a certain place is telling of your inner state of mind consider your own personal feelings and memories with that particular place from what i get out of all this is that when you where younger your life made more scene and it was safer life right now might not be all that you want and you miss what you once had with all your loved ones and a happy place that you all gathered to about you grandfather if you had a special relationship with him then it could be that you are missing him or what he brought to your life what you need to do right now is think of every thing that is missing in your life and try to get it back to where it needs to be so that you can be happy once again i hope that i helped Scenes from a Memory Yoga Sutras of Patanjali One Tree Hill (TV series) Miss Saigon The Amber Spyglass Pitaten Infantilism Cliff Richard Past teac